  "detailed_description": "Minimalist style domino sandbox. Build your domino effect with unlimited pieces, customizable colors and reversibility.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677520/extras/7c8116ad253a9fe0065736ea9df1ee78.poster.avif?t=1758019905\" width=600 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677520/extras/7c8116ad253a9fe0065736ea9df1ee78.webm?t=1758019905\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677520/extras/7c8116ad253a9fe0065736ea9df1ee78.mp4?t=1758019905\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Well-crafted build tool make it fun and easy to try out new ideas.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677520/extras/91c14a77cabd35b906d6e85c36acbffd.poster.avif?t=1758019905\" width=600 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677520/extras/91c14a77cabd35b906d6e85c36acbffd.webm?t=1758019905\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677520/extras/91c14a77cabd35b906d6e85c36acbffd.mp4?t=1758019905\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Minimalist style with maximum customization. Express your artistic mind through the customization feature.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677520/extras/02412bdb0fe79386efcd26914ff50351.poster.avif?t=1758019905\" width=600 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677520/extras/02412bdb0fe79386efcd26914ff50351.webm?t=1758019905\" type=\"